channel.description:
Hello all, my name is Tyler i'm finally releasing my server it will be on 24/7 it's hosted on a VPS. [b][u]NOTE:This is an economy server so keep that in mind![/u][/b] This server will be in beta testing until I fix any bugs you may find. If you do find any bugs please post them on the forums! If not you can always report them to me :P Please come and test this out and at the end of the beta testing I will hold a poll for all that play the server to chose the name of the server :) I don't want to bother uploading any pictures of the server, Only because it's beta testing and I could maybe include pictures when the server is ready for a full release.
Jar Client DOWNLOAD: [url=https://www.dropbox.com/sh/hpkspg25yx0pbel/AABEr0nHMo_AjX_RsHvoJd5Ra?dl=0]https://www.dropbox.com/sh/hpkspg25yx0pbel/AABEr0nHMo_AjX_RsHvoJd5Ra?dl=0[/url] Please feel free to help with the beta testing for all the help I will help think of rewards for finding bugs...ect..
Thank you everyone and I hope you enjoy! [b][i][u][font=arial][size=10pt]ATTENTION!!!!!! You need JRE8 because I compile it using jre8!!![/size][/font][/u][/i][/b]
